OL,3,C'From wheelie bins to overhanging
OL,4,Chedges - there're so many difficult
OL,5,Cobstacles'
OL,7,FIt's calling on people to keep the
OL,8,Fpavements as accessible and safe as
OL,9,Fpossible.
OL,11,FStuart lost his eyesight ten years
OL,12,Fago. Having Olivia by his side means
OL,13,Fhe can be independent and get out of
OL,14,Fthe house.
OL,16,FHe said: "It can be anything from
OL,17,Fwheelie bins, overhanging hedges,
OL,18,Frubbish on the side of the road. In
OL,19,Ftown, things like street furniture not
OL,20,Falways in the best place.
