OL,3,C'From wheelie bins to overhanging
OL,4,Chedges - there're so many difficult
OL,5,Cobstacles'
OL,7,F"There's so many difficult obstacles
OL,8,Fat the moment. There's stuff from
OL,9,FChristmas - all sorts of different
OL,10,Fthings that can cause an issue.
OL,12,F"Olivia will size up what the gap is,
OL,13,Fshe will try to get round it without
OL,14,Fstopping, if she can't, I will put my
OL,15,Fhand out to feel what's there."
OL,17,FNew research conducted by YouGov on
OL,18,Fbehalf of Guide Dogs found eight in 10
OL,19,Fpeople (85%) knew that pavement
OL,20,Fparking impacts the safety of
OL,21,Fpedestrians with a vision impairment.
