OL,5,Cobstacles'
OL,7,FNearly three-quarters (72%) said
OL,8,Fpavement parking is common in their
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,FChris Theobald, policy manager at
OL,12,FGuide Dogs, said: "We've all got to
OL,13,Fshare public space, people don't do
OL,14,Fthis deliberately, it's just about
OL,15,Fbeing considerate.
