OL,3,C'From wheelie bins to overhanging
OL,4,Chedges - there're so many difficult
OL,5,Cobstacles'
OL,7,F"It's been a perfect storm, the
OL,8,Fintroduction of e-scooters, dockless
OL,9,Fbikes plus an increase in pavement
OL,10,Fparking and and increase in people
OL,11,Fusing the streets for commercial
OL,12,Freasons."
OL,14,FThe charity has called on the
OL,15,Fgovernment to introduce national
OL,16,Frestrictions on pavement parking.
